Text: Order Writer Informationnsf Thank you for placing your order for Qwest DSL service You may reference your order for by your billing telephone number During the next two weeks we will be configuring and testing your phone line to ensure that you receive highquality reliable Qwest DSL service It is possible that this testing will identify physical characteristics on your line that will cause your telephone line to be incompatible with Qwest DSL service In this case we will notify you immediately to discuss other options Your Qwest DSL service should be available on Your order
